the swordsman	劍客
Walid, the swordsman, is not pleased.	劍客瓦利德看起來不太高興。
Issur:	伊蘇爾：
the buffed-out blacksmith	那名肌肉發達的鐵匠
The man talking to you is Issur, the blacksmith and weaponer.	跟你說話的人是伊蘇爾，鐵匠兼武器匠。
the spectator	圍觀者
Hassan used to be a Brigand.  Some still wonder.	哈山以前當過強盜。有些人到現在還在懷疑。
Saddam got off duty just to watch Walid beat up on you.	薩達姆特地下班來看瓦利德把你揍一頓。
Hussein was hoping to see Mr. Big-Shot Walid get beaten.	胡笙原本希望能看到大人物瓦利德挨揍。
