the Gateway to the City of Shapeir	夏皮爾城門
This is the Main (and only) gateway to the City of Shapeir.	這是夏皮爾城唯一的主要城門。
the corral	圍欄
The corral is used to keep the sauruses penned in.	這座圍欄用來圈養索魯斯。
the canopy over the saurus lot	索魯斯場上方的遮篷
There is a small canopy for shade and color.	這裡有一個小遮篷，用來遮蔭並增添色彩。
the shade of the awning	遮陽篷的陰影
Only really tall people appreciate the awning's shade.  One can only speculate that it is purely decorative.	只有身材真的很高的人才享受得到這遮陽篷的陰影，看來它純粹是裝飾用的。
Guard Name:	侍衛名字：
The guard looks much like any other well-trained soldier.	這名侍衛看起來就跟其他訓練有素的士兵沒兩樣。
There will be a caravan to Raseir in %u Days.	還有%u天，就會有一支商隊前往拉希爾。
the red saurus	紅色索魯斯
